163.8	An_Inconvenient_Truth	An Inconvenient Truth	An Inconvenient Truth is a 2006 documentary film directed by Davis Guggenheim about former United States Vice President Al Gore's campaign to educate citizens about global warming via a comprehensive slide show that, by his own estimate made in the film, he has given more than a thousand times.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/An_Inconvenient_Truth_Film_Poster.jpg/220px-An_Inconvenient_Truth_Film_Poster.jpg
